  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>SUPRACORE is a <strong>base building roguelike</strong> in which you defend your core from the incoming waves of enemies.<br></li><li>Collect <strong>resources</strong> and keep them in storage units.<br></li><li>Build amazing towers like <strong>Flamethrowers</strong>, <strong>Mortars</strong>, <strong>Cannons</strong> and <strong>Machineguns</strong>.<br></li><li>Collect as many <strong>Powerups</strong> as you can to make your core stronger.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Many structures to research.<br></li><li>Powerful powerups that make each run unique.<br></li><li>A lot of enemies with different abilities.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/deed789e9611c99f42e501bf61ddbe1a.poster.avif?t=1699023173\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/deed789e9611c99f42e501bf61ddbe1a.webm?t=1699023173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/deed789e9611c99f42e501bf61ddbe1a.mp4?t=1699023173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/ad27f9c2e17cc1b998c668b2aac552c9.poster.avif?t=1699023173\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/ad27f9c2e17cc1b998c668b2aac552c9.webm?t=1699023173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433820/extras/ad27f9c2e17cc1b998c668b2aac552c9.mp4?t=1699023173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><